  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to test the routine faisibility of a questionnaire to estimate
      walking impairment(The WELCH questionnaire) in patients investigated for suspected PAD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The WELCH and WIQ questionnaires are self completed by the patients and scored by the
      physician after self-completion.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
